reviews.reviewText: I got this to give for a Christmas present. It is a nice neutral black color and can be used by a man or a woman. reviews.reviewText: This is a great travel bag with plenty of room. A toiletry bag comes as a bonus. The travel set includes a duffel bag and a toiletry bag. The duffel bag is 21" long, 5.9" wide and 9" high. The fabric is soft and durable, waterproof and wear resistant. The bag is easy to clean, lightweight and easy to carry. There are two handles on the top. The duffle bag has several pockets, can easily accommodate travel accessories, clothing, and even shoes. The travel bag has one large, zippered compartment and one small pocket on the side. The roomy toiletry bag has a handle on one side. There are two smaller pockets inside of the duffle bag which are ideal for storing a phone and small articles. I use both bags for a quick weekend getaway. These are also suitable for shopping, gym, camping, and hiking, as well as other outdoor activities.
